<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
  <h2>HTML Text Formatting Examples</h2>
  <p>This is <b>bold text</b>.</p>
  <p>This is <strong>important text</strong>.</p>
  <p>This is <i>italic text</i>.</p>
  <p>This is <em>emphasized text</em>.</p>
  <p>This is <mark>highlighted text</mark>.</p>
  <p>This is <u>underlined text</u>.</p>
  <p>This is <del>deleted text</del> and <ins>inserted text</ins>.</p>
  <p>Chemical Formula: H<sub>2</sub>O</p>
  <p>Mathematical Equation: x<sup>2</sup> + y<sup>2</sup> = z<sup>2</sup></p>
</body>
</html>
